{"tha-ap506:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap506:0.2":"Kanikaravagga ","tha-ap506:0.3":"Avataphaliyattheraapadana ","tha-ap506:1.1":"“Sahassaramsi bhagava, ","tha-ap506:1.2":"sayambhu aparajito; ","tha-ap506:1.3":"Viveka vutthahitvana, ","tha-ap506:1.4":"gocarayabhinikkhami. ","tha-ap506:2.1":"Phalahattho aham disva, ","tha-ap506:2.2":"upagacchim narasabham; ","tha-ap506:2.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap506:2.4":"avatam adadim phalam. ","tha-ap506:3.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap506:3.2":"yam phalam adadim tada; ","tha-ap506:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap506:3.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap506:4.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap506:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap506:4.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap506:5.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap506:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap506:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap506:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap506:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap506:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap506:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma avataphaliyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap506:8.1":"Avataphaliyattherassapadanam catuttham. "}